# === Static web app deploy inputs ===
# Keep the Astro app and prebuilt reader scan assets in git for static hosting.
# `public/source-cache/` is part of the deployed reader because page views load
# WebP scans from that directory.

# === Maintainer workflow docs ===
# Keep agent orchestration and local workflow details private for now; the
# public dataset README carries the user-facing process summary.
AGENT_ORCHESTRATION.md
WORKFLOW.md

